text: Duffy is the nickname of: * Duffy Ayers, English portrait painter born Elizabeth (Betty) Fitzgerald in 1915 * Duffy Cobbs (born 1964), American former football player * Duffy Daugherty (1915–1987), American college football player and Hall of Fame coach * Duffy Dyer (born 1945), American former Major League Baseball player * Duffy Jackson (born 1953), American jazz drummer * Duffy Lewis (1888–1979), American Major League Baseball player * Norma "Duffy" Lyon (1929–2011), American farmer and butter sculptor == See also == * Duffy (disambiguation) * Duffy (surname) Category:Lists of people by nickname
title: Duffy (nickname)
